      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ACOUSTIC BUBBLES (3) missed by 2.5L at this track and trip two back before a 0.4L defeat last time out over further. ZJP now hops on board and she maps beautifully as she looks for her maiden win. Rates highly on her last start and can go one better this time. LOVESEXY (5) led them up over 1100m here last week and was caught late, beaten 0.8L. Faithfull sticks with her today as she inches toward her maiden win. Fitter for that performance and with improvement on the cards, she'll be very tough to run down. QUEEN SELYSE (2) is showing glimpses in her recent efforts and her recent form stacks up in this field. Well placed and won't be far away. IT'S TRICKY (7) is better than she showed last time out and looks better placed coming back to 1200m. Drawn well and can't be discounted. HIDDEN JEWELS (1) won't be be far away.",
